title: Never got my 10 year icon :(
body: I got Riot Kayle, but never the birthday poro icon that celebrated 10 years.

replies.body: Gifts are still being sent out per our current [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Looking into this for you, it looks like you have everything now!  Enjoy the content!
